      <title>蒂努布粮食政策失灵导致尼日利亚大米价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/nigerian-rice-prices-surge-to-record-as-tinubu-s-food-policies-falter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，尼日利亚最受欢迎的乔洛夫米饭的主要原料价格上涨了一倍多，达到历史最高水平，显示出政府在控制这个非洲人口最多国家面临的生活成本危机方面面临重重困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/nigerian-rice-prices-surge-to-record-as-tinubu-s-food-policies-falter</guid>
